00:48:50,309 --> 00:48:53,853
So this awareness that we are exercising

348
00:48:54,340 --> 00:49:22,677
this satipanya, this intuitive intelligence which we're drawing out of it's confusion with the body confusion with confusion meaning together confusion with emotions so when we I am see every time you say I am you've got to say who see who's see you say I am angry who's angry see with thought especially yeah

