00:49:54,675 --> 00:49:54,876
Yeah?

358
00:49:54,896 --> 00:49:56,697
You should all be nodding vigorously.

359
00:49:57,278 --> 00:49:57,539
Yeah?

360
00:49:59,141 --> 00:49:59,920
See?

361
00:49:59,940 --> 00:50:04,326
And the double bind is, you see, how do you get out of that?

362
00:50:06,168 --> 00:50:10,913
Because every time you want to get rid of that sense of self, another self appears to get rid of it.

363
00:50:11,452 --> 00:50:15,376
So you're in an eternal double bind going all the way back

364
00:50:15,981 --> 00:50:40,976
so the Buddha's instructions are to keep averting away from that sense of self that's the delusion, that's the first object we make averting yourself to actually what it is you're experiencing because that's only a concept in the mind it also has a mirror image in the heart as a sense of presence

365
00:50:41,648 --> 00:51:02,255
so often that's described by people as their soul but actually it still belongs to the world of phenomena because it's a feeling and if you have a self-image like the observer that must also still belong to the world of phenomena to the world of feeling, perception etc.

