00:52:15,405 --> 00:52:21,635
When it sees something, the insight, the actual insight is immediate.

370
00:52:22,135 --> 00:52:23,077
There's no thought involved.

371
00:52:23,097 --> 00:52:24,559
You either see it or you don't see it.

372
00:52:25,019 --> 00:52:28,284
But then it has to tell itself what it's just seeing.

373
00:52:30,052 --> 00:52:31,795
And that's where the mind comes in.

374
00:52:31,815 --> 00:52:39,362
The mind has to be used, the intellect is used to refer back to itself what is just observed.

375
00:52:39,382 --> 00:52:49,353
That's why often some of you will have experienced it, but often in meditation a line will come up, just out of the blue, some insight.

