00:52:56,800 --> 00:53:22,976
and it's the if you get hold of his book called the heart straight from the heart these are really beautiful talks although you have to get into the into his way of speaking and there's he's meditating meditating and there just comes this line just out of the blue you see wherever if I can remember it rightly

