00:53:23,293 --> 00:53:33,286
Wherever there arises a sense of a self, that is the beginning of another level of existence, of another level of becoming.

379
00:53:35,068 --> 00:53:41,815
Now, what he's saying there is, as soon as the I appears, there's a process happens.

380
00:53:42,556 --> 00:53:50,465
And if that I, because of the I, of the delusion of I, there's always going to be some dissatisfaction involved.

381
00:53:51,003 --> 00:54:20,436
because this I is always seeking real happiness in the sensual world and it won't deliver and with that insight he seems as though he really moved now that came from this intuitive intelligence telling itself what it's just seeing it happens to us in ordinary daily life when suddenly you say something amazingly wise

