00:54:24,295 --> 00:54:24,695
Yes.

385
00:54:24,795 --> 00:54:24,956
No.

386
00:54:27,940 --> 00:54:32,186
You suddenly find yourself giving advice to somebody and you wonder how the heck you came across that.

