391
00:55:02,284 --> 00:55:17,405
And when it came to questions about the soul, you see, there's a lovely one where this man Vajagota comes up, and he's completely confused, and he goes to Buddha and he says, now come on, is there a soul or isn't there, you see?

392
00:55:18,989 --> 00:55:21,233
He's obviously had discussions with this and that.

393
00:55:21,253 --> 00:55:23,356
He's had discussions with the Buddha and he's finally fed up.

394
00:55:23,657 --> 00:55:26,141
He says, look, come on, I want to know, is there a soul?

395
00:55:26,521 --> 00:55:27,702
